Install LCM:

	delete lock (https://askubuntu.com/questions/15433/unable-to-lock-the-administration-directory-var-lib-dpkg-is-another-process)
	
	update to glib 2.0 (sudo apt-get install libglib2.0-dev) 
	
	./configure
	make
	sudo make install

	sudo ldconfig (after a new installation)



installed rosserial, rosserial for arduino

If unable to boot, in bios change optimazed setting or default fail safe setting, then try again




